{"tid":948910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵5款月票明年1月起加價5至10元　車費扣減亦結束","createTime":"2018-12-20T12:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T13:24:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e86590098ce8cd5292e1b7c81806c9e3be90e3ad","tid":948910,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，5款月票下月起加價，加價介乎10至15元，而「程程3%車費扣減」優惠的推廣期，亦會在下月完結。<br />\n<br />\n民間監管公共事業聯委會發言人蔡耀昌批評，今次港鐵除了月票加價，連同優惠亦取消，意味全部乘客都會受影響，認為加價是不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434324-20181220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434324-20181220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0pJ34ZEMQy7P7%2FdOqtSk7xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a468e7b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434324-20181220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=93d5511f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434324-20181220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b643cbe6be8babc2c1cff3e2b8d7b3d85be7c223","tid":948910,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181220/_2018122017132123365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181220%2F_2018122017132123365.jpg&h=4bd04dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵宣佈，5款「全月通加強版」、「港鐵都會票」及「屯門－南昌全日通」，將於明年1月起加價。<br />\n<br />\n「港鐵都會票」及「屯門－南昌全日通」的售價將於明年1月2日起加價，「港鐵都會票」將由425元加至435元，而「屯門－南昌全日通」則將由由27元加至28元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，「全月通加強版」亦將於明年1月起加價，「東涌&ndash;香港全月通加強版」將由620元加到635元；「東涌&ndash;南昌全月通加強版」由395元加到405元；「上水/烏溪沙&ndash;尖東全月通加強版」由475元加到485元；「屯門&ndash;南昌全月通加強版」由500元加到515元；「屯門&ndash;紅磡全月通加強版」則由585元加到600元。<br />\n<br />\n至於港鐵現時的「程程3%車費扣減」優惠亦將於明年元旦日完結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1392882/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1392882%2F&d=0pJ34ZEMQy7P7%2FdOqtSk7xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d8910b07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1392882%2F&h=940a32a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1392882/</a>"},{"pid":"4171c753589f040e98b78d923489478635e52fff","tid":948910,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"罰左800萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f065377b3b41e5a35de614f76e2ad6149d3f57","tid":948910,"uid":33878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:09:42.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n張減價表阻住我睇腳呀dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無無表格版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e236d5ec7439116efffc510e0cfbc1dfacf8eb13","tid":948910,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80d2d36aaecc7e9f3b4a60a6523163804be04cc","tid":948910,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"屌！"},{"pid":"bdeda641b4c14e5e49e77aa8da6b0deb4e497017","tid":948910,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"馬屎坑 「唔加價點補貼沙中線單野 ?  」"},{"pid":"c062ce900197ac77d71f803749bb3212ed81152c","tid":948910,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母狗鐵"},{"pid":"e0b59ec6624c8d45ff627276ef4dcb892f159794","tid":948910,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾成撚日加"},{"pid":"b3a0b71ed5353e8120998de63353f009a416c5db","tid":948910,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"